  "detailed_description": "<strong>Many years ago,</strong> There was a legend about ancient relics, It was said that the holder of the relics can manipulate time itself and become the time master. I spent years searching for the relics map, But one day I woke up and found it in my hand, Machines started coming from the future. All we know that they are made to protect the timeline, They call them Paradox Guardians. The Timeline resets after mystery event that happens in every Timeline at same Time frame.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MOVAFORT</h2> is a place where you can Travel Through time Without limits, You can Travel to the future or the past to Change the Timeline.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b7a43b02b7614ab3a55624f34796ca19.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b7a43b02b7614ab3a55624f34796ca19.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b7a43b02b7614ab3a55624f34796ca19.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MOVAFORT WORLDS </h2>MOVAFORT Contains 2 Worlds with large number of <strong>Biomes</strong>, Each have unique Landscape, Loot, Enemies and Villages.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/6d885768d2a4afec85bad3c9ec6eac66.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/6d885768d2a4afec85bad3c9ec6eac66.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/6d885768d2a4afec85bad3c9ec6eac66.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STOP THE PARADOX</h2>Embark on a journey to discover the mystery of the <strong>Timeline </strong>events and Save the world from its Loop Prison.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/c36e7120b51943b83294bc31507bcd7c.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/c36e7120b51943b83294bc31507bcd7c.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/c36e7120b51943b83294bc31507bcd7c.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOOT, CRAFT AND SURVIVE</h2><strong>Trade, Steal, or Craft.</strong> Choose what suits you with A large number of Tools, Potions and Weapons. Choose your items but be careful, You Can’t carry items to the past without causing a paradox.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/bd1e6a575444a57c3d66bfe6b316a86f.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/bd1e6a575444a57c3d66bfe6b316a86f.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/bd1e6a575444a57c3d66bfe6b316a86f.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Paradox Will Find You</h2>Time Doesn’t like manipulators. When it comes to time travel one thing can't exist More than Once at the same time. Bringing item from the future to the past will result in a <strong>Paradox</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/f5c28c9f44403c806d02e7e4281b5613.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/f5c28c9f44403c806d02e7e4281b5613.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/f5c28c9f44403c806d02e7e4281b5613.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Open <strong>Time Travel</strong> Where you can travel to the future or the past.<ul class=\"bb_ul\">- <strong>Massive World</strong> where every Biome is unique, With different robots, Villages, Items and recipes to discover.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Large Number of <strong>items with upgrades</strong> and skills makes your choice count.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- <strong>Trade </strong>with Villagers or buy from the shops and find rare items.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- <strong>Stealth </strong>is an option when it comes to hide from Guardians or steal from Villagers while they are sleeping.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Massive <strong>Crafting </strong>system where recipes are discovered as you explore the world and pick-up new resources and ingredients.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Challenging <strong>Elites Battles</strong>.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Create, Play & Share <strong>Challenges</strong> with your Own Rules<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b836faf20e40fbd3283d5ba5baf5315e.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b836faf20e40fbd3283d5ba5baf5315e.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b836faf20e40fbd3283d5ba5baf5315e.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Many years ago,</strong> There was a legend about ancient relics, It was said that the holder of the relics can manipulate time itself and become the time master. I spent years searching for the relics map, But one day I woke up and found it in my hand, Machines started coming from the future. All we know that they are made to protect the timeline, They call them Paradox Guardians. The Timeline resets after mystery event that happens in every Timeline at same Time frame.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MOVAFORT</h2> is a place where you can Travel Through time Without limits, You can Travel to the future or the past to Change the Timeline.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b7a43b02b7614ab3a55624f34796ca19.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b7a43b02b7614ab3a55624f34796ca19.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b7a43b02b7614ab3a55624f34796ca19.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MOVAFORT WORLDS </h2>MOVAFORT Contains 2 Worlds with large number of <strong>Biomes</strong>, Each have unique Landscape, Loot, Enemies and Villages.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/6d885768d2a4afec85bad3c9ec6eac66.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/6d885768d2a4afec85bad3c9ec6eac66.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/6d885768d2a4afec85bad3c9ec6eac66.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STOP THE PARADOX</h2>Embark on a journey to discover the mystery of the <strong>Timeline </strong>events and Save the world from its Loop Prison.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/c36e7120b51943b83294bc31507bcd7c.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/c36e7120b51943b83294bc31507bcd7c.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/c36e7120b51943b83294bc31507bcd7c.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOOT, CRAFT AND SURVIVE</h2><strong>Trade, Steal, or Craft.</strong> Choose what suits you with A large number of Tools, Potions and Weapons. Choose your items but be careful, You Can’t carry items to the past without causing a paradox.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/bd1e6a575444a57c3d66bfe6b316a86f.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/bd1e6a575444a57c3d66bfe6b316a86f.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/bd1e6a575444a57c3d66bfe6b316a86f.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Paradox Will Find You</h2>Time Doesn’t like manipulators. When it comes to time travel one thing can't exist More than Once at the same time. Bringing item from the future to the past will result in a <strong>Paradox</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/f5c28c9f44403c806d02e7e4281b5613.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/f5c28c9f44403c806d02e7e4281b5613.webm?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/f5c28c9f44403c806d02e7e4281b5613.mp4?t=1745509453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Open <strong>Time Travel</strong> Where you can travel to the future or the past.<ul class=\"bb_ul\">- <strong>Massive World</strong> where every Biome is unique, With different robots, Villages, Items and recipes to discover.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Large Number of <strong>items with upgrades</strong> and skills makes your choice count.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- <strong>Trade </strong>with Villagers or buy from the shops and find rare items.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- <strong>Stealth </strong>is an option when it comes to hide from Guardians or steal from Villagers while they are sleeping.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Massive <strong>Crafting </strong>system where recipes are discovered as you explore the world and pick-up new resources and ingredients.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Challenging <strong>Elites Battles</strong>.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Create, Play & Share <strong>Challenges</strong> with your Own Rules<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b836faf20e40fbd3283d5ba5baf5315e.poster.avif?t=1745509453\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079600/extras/b836faf20e40fbd3283d5ba5baf